{"tid":1192894,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)V煞 幽靈空間","createTime":"2019-06-08T16:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T18:45:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10fb30dfc95d1f415da72402e09ca03839078940","tid":1192894,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=5411369c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=c22e7b05\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=af156098\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/11/V_for_Vendetta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F11%2FV_for_Vendetta.jpg&h=3b449eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/71/Spectral_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F71%2FSpectral_Poster.jpg&h=4e465d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.該片的背景設定在2020年[8]，此時的英國由一個受法西斯政黨「北方之火」控制的極權政府統治。艾薇&middot;哈蒙德是一名年輕的勞工階級女子，在一次違反宵禁外出時遭一群「Fingermen」成員圍堵，當他們正欲圖謀不軌之時，一名戴著蓋&middot;福克斯面具的男子將艾薇從他們的手中救了出來。他自稱「V」。隨後，被政府視作恐怖分子的V帶著艾薇登上了附近一座建築的屋頂，觀賞他在柴可夫斯基的《1812序曲》的伴奏中炸毀老貝利街的場景。恐慌的獨裁當局向民眾宣稱這是一次政府事先計劃的舊樓爆破。但很快，V就潛入國營電視台&mdash;&mdash;英國電視網（BTN），透過當局的宣傳機器澄清了真相。同時，V呼籲全英國的民眾在一年後的11月5日站出來，與他一起在英國國會大廈前示威以反抗獨裁統治，並暗示他將在那一天摧毀國會大廈<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述在一座戰亂的歐洲城市，一支三角洲部隊駐守於此，但他們發現某種無形的神秘生物潛伏於周遭，並接連殺害他們的士兵。使得一名工程師與該部隊必須為了存活，而與看不見的敵人戰鬥。 <br />\n<br />\n1 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b1c07b90\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=07f9012d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a>"},{"pid":"4fa5bba31e9f895a0db9e02fcaed20443ea94e10","tid":1192894,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59ef93fd651316604b3c0694baa11a226888f81","tid":1192894,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.